Gather around.

01:00.600 --> 01:02.520
We got another tradition
starting this Christmas.

01:02.700 --> 01:05.300
All of y'all get to ask
your mother for one thing

01:05.319 --> 01:07.400
she can put under the
tree for y'all to open

01:07.500 --> 01:08.879
on Christmas morning.

01:08.880 --> 01:11.019
Within reason, all right?

01:11.020 --> 01:12.939
Don't go asking me for no damn Subaru.

01:12.940 --> 01:14.880
- I-I want...
- Uh-uh-uh. I want

01:14.900 --> 01:18.260
python high-top sneakers
with the snakeskin.

01:18.340 --> 01:19.790
You can't yell it out like that,

01:19.820 --> 01:21.216
- like we on The Price is Right.
- Mm-hmm.

01:21.240 --> 01:23.320
You need to write a note
to your Mother Santa,

01:23.380 --> 01:25.790
put it under the tree so she can find.

01:25.890 --> 01:27.260
- Angel.
- Hmm?

01:27.320 --> 01:28.860
Please write your note.

01:30.860 --> 01:33.460
I told you I didn't want
anything for Christmas.

01:33.560 --> 01:34.660
It's Christmas. I mean,

01:34.770 --> 01:36.870
everybody wants something, right?

01:45.260 --> 01:47.080
When I was six years old,

01:48.160 --> 01:50.260
my father took me with him
to the department store

01:50.300 --> 01:52.120
to buy some Christmas presents.

01:52.620 --> 01:54.519
I saw this one pair of

01:54.520 --> 01:57.400
red pumps with a four-inch heel.

02:01.320 --> 02:03.040
I swear to God,

02:04.080 --> 02:07.700
I had never seen anything quite
so beautiful in my entire life.

02:08.400 --> 02:10.139
When no one was looking,

02:10.280 --> 02:11.770
I took one,

02:11.870 --> 02:13.600
snuck it home,

02:13.700 --> 02:16.560
hidden underneath my coat.

02:16.580 --> 02:18.540
When we got to the apartment,

02:18.740 --> 02:20.820
I tried running straight to my room.

02:22.240 --> 02:24.280
It slipped out and fell onto the floor,

02:24.400 --> 02:26.580
right in front of my
mother and my father.

02:28.980 --> 02:31.600
I begged them to let me keep it.

02:37.530 --> 02:39.140
My father s...

02:41.040 --> 02:44.280
my father slapped me across the face.

02:49.420 --> 02:50.800
For stealing.

02:52.360 --> 02:54.400
But more so for what I chose to steal.

02:57.820 --> 03:00.480
I mean, what kind of little boy

03:00.500 --> 03:03.640
