07:40.980 --> 07:43.620
- It was my grandmother's.
- Don't bullshit me.

07:43.700 --> 07:45.180
That offends me.

07:49.390 --> 07:52.519
I mopped it, from a
coat check in midtown.

07:52.520 --> 07:53.980
I just wanted to get a trophy,

07:54.020 --> 07:56.000
so I-I borrowed it. But
I'm gonna take it back.

07:56.060 --> 07:58.680
That's not what Evangelista's about.

08:01.960 --> 08:03.500
Let's get something straight.

08:03.600 --> 08:05.330
I'm not running a halfway home.

08:05.430 --> 08:07.720
We're a family, and I'm
building a legacy.

08:07.880 --> 08:10.070
I'll admit, you got something special,

08:10.170 --> 08:11.599
but you're cocky.

08:11.600 --> 08:13.420
Judges don't want arrogance,
they want confidence.

08:13.440 --> 08:15.280
If you want to win grand prize,

08:15.380 --> 08:17.780
