15:14.740 --> 15:16.300
Would you close your eyes for me?

15:18.740 --> 15:20.130
Okay...

15:36.320 --> 15:37.900
Open.

15:46.000 --> 15:47.080
We got, uh...

15:48.160 --> 15:50.880
