15:51.000 --> 15:52.720
Microwave, toaster.

15:52.820 --> 15:56.120
We got, uh, all new Formica countertops.

15:57.560 --> 15:58.800
Dusty.

16:00.240 --> 16:02.480
I got the, um...

16:02.960 --> 16:04.879
... the TV and VCR, they're on order.

16:04.880 --> 16:07.240
T-That should be, uh,
arriving next week.

16:08.150 --> 16:09.420
Over there.

16:13.260 --> 16:17.800
This is so beautiful.

16:22.560 --> 16:24.920
Wow.

16:26.230 --> 16:28.070
Oh, my God.

16:43.020 --> 16:44.960
I don't know what to say.

16:49.320 --> 16:50.940
I feel so safe here.

16:53.040 --> 16:55.430
