17:16.780 --> 17:19.290
even just for an hour.

17:20.960 --> 17:22.680
For a glass of eggnog,

17:22.740 --> 17:24.660
or whatever.

17:26.540 --> 17:29.360
It would really make this
place feel like a home to me.

17:29.880 --> 17:31.560
Of course I will.

17:42.410 --> 17:44.180
Mm.

